description: This datatype is used to store the time profiling information of any service or component.

componentName.title: componentName
componentName.description: The name of the service/component, for which time information is captured.

serviceGroup.title: serviceGroup
serviceGroup.description: An optional attribute, to capture the timeline of a service, at sub-tree level.

startTime.title: startTime
startTime.description: Execution Start time in Date-Time format for the component.

endTime.title: endTime
endTime.description: Execution End time in Date-Time format for the component.
